uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974672_643693450068372_2765381301779825349_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VJIvjFeH0IwQ7kNvgGxT4g7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAWGNdToBVsVzPkPuuaL6zB8Kkkbhq-PmUfCnRm04wiJQ&oe=67430A8E"}, {"file_name": "4.png", "id": "535137037942845", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974817_535137041276178_8615470723784735579_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=SBlU2eeGgQgQ7kNvgFywRYc&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBAVd6T4WnZvWx4RLBOp6OMti6ssxSLQzVikKrB-tRmrw&oe=67432981"}, {"file_name": "2.png", "id": "378241330781577", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974584_378241334114910_3487644665188837393_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4JkvzB0UUoYQ7kNvgHk6rej&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBfAK7fZgKzQerNZQZGBafrnAz2xQn72tNLETof0tKU8Q&oe=67430782"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "LANDSCAPE_2560x1440.png", "id": "1680606845623142", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974584_1680606848956475_6020773676294071676_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=r9O29jUCPxUQ7kNvgFbs2Lc&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDlRKBmRvFFkjHquchGfJcE_i4ZyQNRF1Hw1JJ3lZlQQg&oe=67431BD7"}, "display_name": "Dungeon Maker", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Greetings My Lord ! \ud83d\udc51\n\nI hath heard thou art quite the dungeon connoisseur, so i maketh this bawbling passthrough system where thee can buildeth thy owneth dungeon using a variety of traps and items, as well as lodging waypoints to giveth goals to the dungeon seekers. \ud83c\udff0\n\nWhat can I expect from my dungeon??\nFear not Sire, there is much:\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Proceduraly generated plot and a treasure to go with it.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Hand tracking and presence! Use your hands to bring up your Orb of Quests as well as interact with the world.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 A variety of slashing, crushing and deadly traps.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Lava floor!\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Quest items such as waypoints and keys (that open doors).\n6\ufe0f\u20e3 Occlusion boxes to occlude your own furniture.\n7\ufe0f\u20e3 Walls to build around your dungeon.\n8\ufe0f\u20e3 A save / load system so you don't need to keep rebuilding each time! (Even tough it's fun to build, let's be honest.)", "short_description": "Build your own Dungeon in your home using Passthrough!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.fieldof.vision/PrivacyPolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Field Of Vision", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://fieldof.vision/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1990104051447093"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "ACTION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "355455956363606"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "303868631890285"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "303868631890285"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1650124800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "303868631890285"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "9287942507883581", "version": "0.32.0"}, "id": "482044523410394", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5379303768747494", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9287942507883581"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "482044523410394"}]}, "change_log": "Version 0.32\n- Added windows that see into the exerior bleak world!\n- Changed room portal design, added frame and is blocked off if there's no connecting room setup.\n- Added loading screen on menu when loading or starting a new dungeon.\n\nVersion 0.31\n- 90FPS on Quest3/3S!\n- Redesigned the menu from the ground up.\n- You can now easily switch between left/right handed in the new menu settings.\n- Settings also include toggling controller button tips!\n- Added 3D controllers while in the menu for easier visiblity, and for tips to make sense.\n- Added function to duplicate items directly, no need to keep going back to the menu!\n- The dungeon foundation now includes all rooms instead of just current room. \n- A portal is placed on your doors that lead to another setup room, though make sure your physical doors are open ^^. (Try blocking access to the portal with the Door & Key quest item!)\n- Added particles effects to certain items like the key, treasure and waypoints.\n- The app is now boundaryless, which means you no longer need see or setup a boundary to use it. Really helps when going through multiple rooms!\n- There's also a tab in the menu with some of my other games, check them out!\n- You can no longer portal to the current dungeon, a message will warn you that you are selecting the same dungeon.\n- Creating a new dungeon doesn't increment the dungeon number until it's been saved.\n- Removed the limit to how many Dungeons you can save.\n- When you start a dungeon adventure, it'll be automatically saved.\n- You now have to place the Starting point\n- Ceiling traps now snap to the ceiling so it's easier to drag and place them correctly.", "created_date": 1731919077, "id": "9287942507883581", "version": "0.32.0", "version_code": 22, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5379303768747494", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9287942507883581"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "482044523410394"}]}, "change_log": "NEW STUFF:\n- 90FPS on Quest3/3S!\n- Redesigned the menu from the ground up.\n- You can now easily switch between left/right handed in the new menu settings.\n- Settings also include toggling controller button tips!\n- Added 3D controllers while in the menu for easier visiblity, and for tips to make sense.\n- Added function to duplicate items directly, no need to keep going back to the menu!\n- The dungeon foundation now includes all rooms instead of just current room. \n- A portal is placed on your doors that lead to another setup room, though make sure your physical doors are open ^^. (Try blocking access to the portal with the Door & Key quest item!)\n- Added particles effects to certain items like the key, treasure and waypoints.\n- The app is now boundaryless, which means you no longer need see or setup a boundary to use it. Really helps when going through multiple rooms!\n- There's also a tab in the menu with some of my other games, check them out!\n\n\nFIXES:\n- You can no longer portal to the current dungeon, a message will warn you that you are selecting the same dungeon.\n- Creating a new dungeon doesn't increment the dungeon number until it's been saved.\n- Removed the limit to how many Dungeons you can save.\n- When you start a dungeon adventure, it'll be automatically saved.\n- You now have to place the Starting point\n- Ceiling traps now snap to the ceiling so it's easier to drag and place them correctly.", "created_date": 1731723334, "id": "9275619485782550", "version": "0.31.1", "version_code": 21, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5379303768747494", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9287942507883581"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1731723101, "id": "9275593675785131", "version": "0.31.1", "version_code": 20, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5379303768747494", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9287942507883581"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "482044523410394"}]}, "change_log": "NEW STUFF:\n- 90FPS on Quest3/3S!\n- Redesigned the menu from the ground up.\n- You can now easily switch between left/right handed in the new menu settings.\n- Settings also include toggling controller button tips!\n- Added 3D controllers while in the menu for easier visiblity, and for tips to make sense.\n- Added function to duplicate items directly, no need to keep going back to the menu!\n- The dungeon foundation now includes all rooms instead of just current room. \n- A portal is placed on your doors that lead to another setup room, though make sure your physical doors are open ^^. (Try blocking access to the portal with the Door & Key quest item!)\n- Added particles effects to certain items like the key, treasure and waypoints.\n- The app is now boundaryless, which means you no longer need see or setup a boundary to use it. Really helps when going through multiple rooms!\n- There's also a tab in the menu with some of my other games, check them out!\n\n\nFIXES:\n- You can no longer portal to the current dungeon, a message will warn you that you are selecting the same dungeon.\n- Creating a new dungeon doesn't increment the dungeon number until it's been saved.\n- Removed the limit to how many Dungeons you can save.\n- When you start a dungeon adventure, it'll be automatically saved.\n- You now have to place the Starting point\n- Ceiling traps now snap to the ceiling so it's easier to drag and place them correctly.", "created_date": 1731392840, "id": "9247000448644454", "version": "0.31.0", "version_code": 19, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5379303768747494", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9287942507883581"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "482044523410394"}]}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1730364137, "id": "9164342530243580", "version": "0.30.0", "version_code": 18, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileA